        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Standard greeting: &apos;As-salamu alaykum&apos; (peace be upon you), reply &apos;Wa alaykum as-salam&apos;. Handshakes common between same gender. Wait for woman to extend hand first. Cheek kisses among friends (same gender).</rdfs:comment>
