        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Restaurants: 10% if service not included. Hotels: 1-2 JOD for porters. Guides: 5-10 JOD per day. Taxi: round up fare. Tour drivers: 3-5 JOD per day.</rdfs:comment>
